{"tid":1885080,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"武肺還未傳出中國，北韓斷絕一切來往；日本人表示歡迎支那春節遊客。","createTime":"2020-02-18T04:56:59.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-18T13:46:09.000Z","uid":1589,"like":29,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"69df173da833f4e76e73ce58fac3bf6d621d4bfa","tid":1885080,"uid":1589,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-18T04:56:59.000Z","msg":"武肺還未傳出中國，北韓斷絕一切來往；日本人表示歡迎支那春節遊客。<br />\nWHO未升級做緊急狀態，台灣開始封關；日本商人好奇口罩為什麼好賣。<br />\n武漢封城，澳門趕急封關口，安倍開始計劃送住武漢既日本人返日本。<br />\nWHO提出緊急狀態，美帝拿拿臨封關，日本人開始關注旅遊收入減少。<br />\n世界各地出現口罩荒，香港人自救；日本人捐口罩比支那「姊妹城市」。<br />\n鑽石公主號船上3700人出現疫情，香港；美國；加拿大開始撤僑；日本政府表示一日只能驗300個樣本。<br />\n亞洲疫情無法控制，香港、台灣、澳門宣佈全民不準外出；日本人繼續搭鐵返工。<br />\n世界疫情無法控制，奧運因無國家願意出席而取消；日本人終於說：『老天，武肺好像真的很可怕！』<br />\n安倍：『最近好像少了中國遊客！』<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">抵撚死</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n利申：<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">（好撚後悔）</span>居日"},{"pid":"91a602b57f7bffb444d77bf91bf4fd351fc1933c","tid":1885080,"uid":1589,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-18T04:59:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mpn6WPg.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fmpn6WPg.png&h=5bf8749c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/O0LPUAX.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FO0LPUAX.png&h=65b78780&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/U0AkgPi.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FU0AkgPi.png&h=da0cfb15&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4886540c25e4d51cfa1ce9a917ad440b1204921e","tid":1885080,"uid":6532,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-18T05:02:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"222ceaca5b823458bdcafee2ae6beba7f7d0bcc3","t